Package org.bicycleGeometryWorkshop.attributes

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AttributeChangeListener
    Listener interface for attribute changes.
    AttributeSetOwner
    Listener interface for AttributeSets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeChangeEvent
    Event Object for a change in Attribute.
    AttributeEditor
    This class serves as the container for the an individual Attribute Editor.
    AttributeSet
    This class is a set of all the attributes associated with a BaseComponent.
    AttributeSetPanel
    JPanel class for displaying Attribute Editors.
    AttributeSetScrollPane
    This class wraps the AttributeSetPanel for display in the UI.
    BaseAttribute
    Attribute base class.
    BooleanAttribute
    Attribute to contain a boolean value.
    BooleanAttributeEditor
    This is the editor class for a Boolean attribute (JCheckBox).
    ColorAttribute
    Attribute to hold a color value with alpha.
    ColorAttributeEditor
    This is the editor class for a color attribute.
    DoubleAttribute
    Attribute to hold a double value.
    DoubleAttributeEditor
    This is the editor class for a double attribute.
    EnumAttribute
    Attribute to hold an Enum value.
    EnumAttributeEditor
    Editor for EnumAttributes.
    LengthAttribute
    Attribute to hold a length.
    LengthAttributeEditor
    This is the editor class for the length attribute.
    StringAttribute
    Attribute to hold a string.
    StringAttributeEditor
    This is the editor class for the string attribute.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AttributeDataType
    This is the enumerator for the data type used in the database.
